description: WisdomTree Long CHF Short EUR 3x Daily is designed to provide investors with a 'leveraged long' exposure to Swiss Franc (CHF) relative to Euro (EUR) by tracking the MSFX Triple Long Swiss Franc/Euro Index (TR) (the Index), which aims to reflect three times the performance of a position in forward contracts which are rolled on a daily basis.
name: WisdomTree Long CHF Short EUR 3x Daily
